# Milk Parlour Customer Dashboard (Next.js)

- Use **Next.js App Router** with **TypeScript** and **Tailwind CSS**.
- Visual style is **mobile-first**, clean, modern, using **Fresh Green + White** as primary colors.
- Use **`lucide-react`** for icons (avoid other icon packs unless asked).

## Data rules (no mock data)

- Never use mock/static placeholder data for real screens.
- All data must be fetched from the live Python backend at `http://127.0.0.1:8000`.
- Prefer server-side fetching in server components when possible; use client fetching only when necessary (interactions, real-time updates).
